\noindent{\bf Best L3X Config at Stage 2.}
The strong AUC of {\em amp} is a strong
starting point for the {\em thr}
classifier at Stage 2, where it achieves the best R@P values, with almost 50% for R@P50---with a large margin over the second-best method.